window.docContents[72].resolve({"/_________Monad-___--do--_________/API-______/#zh-monads-api-root":{"contents":"除了此处描述的一般函数之外，还有一些函数通常定义为每个集合类型的命名空间中的 API 的一部分：\n\n* mapM 映射一元函数。* forM 映射一个单子函数，丢弃结果。* filterM 使用一元谓词进行过滤，返回满足它的值。\n\nMonadic Collection OperationsArray.filterM 可用于编写依赖于副作用的过滤器。def values := #[1, 2, 3, 5, 8]\ndef main : IO Unit := do\n  let filtered ← values.filterM fun v => do\n    repeat\n      IO.println s!\"Keep {v}? [y/n]\"\n      let answer := (← (← IO.getStdin).getLine).trimAscii.copy\n      if answer == \"y\" then return true\n      if answer == \"n\" then return false\n    return false\n  IO.println \"These values were kept:\"\n  for v in filtered do\n    IO.println s!\" * {v}\"\ny\nn\noops\ny\nn\ny\nKeep 1? [y/n]\nKeep 2? [y/n]\nKeep 3? [y/n]\nKeep 3? [y/n]\nKeep 5? [y/n]\nKeep 8? [y/n]\nThese values were kept:\n * 1\n * 3\n * 8\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n","context":"Lean 参考\u0009函子、Monad 和  do  表示法","header":"18.4. API 参考","id":"/_________Monad-___--do--_________/API-______/#zh-monads-api-root"},"/____________/___/#quasiquotation":{"contents":"Quasiquotation 是一种可能包含 antiquotations 的引用形式，反引用 是未引用的引用区域，而是计算结果语法的表达式。\n准引用本质上是一个模板；外部引用区域提供了一个固定的框架，始终产生相同的外部语法，而反引号产生最终语法中不同的部分。\nLean 中的所有引用都是准引用，因此不需要特殊语法来区分准引用和其他引用。\n引用过程不会将宏作用域添加到通过反引号插入的标识符，因为这些标识符要么来自另一个引用（在这种情况下它们已经具有宏作用域），要么来自宏的输入（在这种情况下它们不应该具有宏作用域，因为它们不是由宏引入的）。\n\n基本反引号由美元符号 ($) 和紧随其后的标识符组成。\n这意味着相应变量的值（应该是语法树）将被替换到引用语法的这个位置。\n通过将整个表达式括在括号中，可以将其用作反引号。\n\n\n\n\n\nLean 的解析器根据解析器在给定位置的期望为每个反引号分配一个语法类别。\n如果解析器需要语法类别 c，则反引号的类型为 TSyntax c。\n\n某些语法类别可以与其他类别的元素相匹配。\n例如，数字和字符串文字除了是它们自己的语法类别之外，也是有效的术语。\n反引号可以通过在反引号后面加上冒号和类别名称来注释预期类别，这会导致解析器验证带注释的类别在给定位置是否可接受，并构造解析树中所需的任何中间层。\n\nAntiquotations启动反引号的美元符号（“$”）与后面的标识符或括号内的术语之间不允许有空格。\n同样，注释反引号的语法类别的冒号周围不允许有空格。\n\nQuasiquotation本例中使用了两种形式的反引号。\n由于自然数不是语法，因此 quote 用于将数字转换为表示它的语法。open Lean in\nexample [Monad m] [MonadQuotation m] (x : Term) (n : Nat) : m Syntax :=\n  `($x + $(quote (n + 2)))\n\n\nAntiquotation Annotations此示例要求 m 是一个可以进行报价的 monad。variable {m : Type → Type} [Monad m] [MonadQuotation m]\n默认情况下，反引号 $e 应该是一个术语，因为这是立即预期作为加法的第二个参数的语法类别。def ex1 (e) := show m _ from `(2 + $e)\n#check ex1\nex1 {m : Type → Type} [Monad m] [MonadQuotation m] (e : TSyntax `term) : m (TSyntax `term)\n将 $e 注释为数字文字会成功，因为数字文字也是有效术语。\n参数 e 的预期类型更改为 TSyntax `num。def ex2 (e) := show m _ from `(2 + $e:num)\n#check ex2\nex2 {m : Type → Type} [Monad m] [MonadQuotation m] (e : TSyntax `num) : m (TSyntax `term)\n美元符号和标识符之间不允许有空格。def ex2 (e) := show m _ from `(2 + $ e:num)\n<example>:1:34-1:36: unexpected token '$'; expected '`(tactic|' or no space before spliced term\n冒号之前也不允许有空格：def ex2 (e) := show m _ from `(2 + $e :num)\n<example>:1:37-1:39: unexpected token ':'; expected ')'\n\n\n\n\nExpanding Quasiquotation打印 f 的定义演示了准引用的扩展。open Lean in\ndef f [Monad m] [MonadQuotation m]\n    (x : Term) (n : Nat) : m Syntax :=\n  `(fun k => $x + $(quote (n + 2)) + k)\n#print f\ndef f : {m : Type → Type} → [Monad m] → [Lean.MonadQuotation m] → Lean.Term → Nat → m Syntax :=\nfun {m} [Monad m] [Lean.MonadQuotation m] x n => do\n  let info ← Lean.MonadRef.mkInfoFromRefPos\n  let scp ← Lean.getCurrMacroScope\n  let quotCtx ← Lean.MonadQuotation.getContext\n  pure\n      {\n          raw :=\n            Syntax.node2 info `Lean.Parser.Term.fun (Syntax.atom info \"fun\")\n              (Syntax.node4 info `Lean.Parser.Term.basicFun\n                (Syntax.node1 info `null (Syntax.ident info \"k\".toRawSubstring' (Lean.addMacroScope quotCtx `k scp) []))\n                (Syntax.node info `null #[]) (Syntax.atom info \"=>\")\n                (Syntax.node3 info `«term_+_»\n                  (Syntax.node3 info `«term_+_» x.raw (Syntax.atom info \"+\") (Lean.quote `term (n + 2)).raw)\n                  (Syntax.atom info \"+\")\n                  (Syntax.ident info \"k\".toRawSubstring' (Lean.addMacroScope quotCtx `k scp) []))) }.raw\n在此输出中，报价是 do 块。\n它首先构建结果语法的源信息，这些信息是通过向编译器查询当前正在处理的用户语法而获得的。\n然后，它获取当前宏作用域和正在处理的模块的名称，因为宏作用域是相对于模块添加的，以实现独立编译并避免需要全局计数器。\n然后，它使用 Syntax.node1 和 Syntax.node2 等帮助器构造一个节点，这些帮助器创建一个具有指定数量的子节点的 Syntax.node。\n宏作用域被添加到每个标识符，并且 TSyntax.raw 用于提取类型化语法包装器的内容。\nx 和 quote (n + 2) 的反引号直接出现在扩展中，作为 Syntax.node3 的参数。\n\n","context":"Lean 参考\u0009符号和宏\u0009宏\u0009引述","header":"23.5.3.1. 准报价","id":"/____________/___/#quasiquotation"},"/____________/______/#zh-basictypes-int-h007":{"contents":"通常，使用 Lean 的重载算术表示法来访问整数的算术运算。\n特别是，Add Int、Neg Int、Sub Int 和 Mul Int 的实例允许使用普通中缀运算符。\n除法 稍微复杂一些，因为整数除法有多种合理的概念。\n\nAddition of integers, usually accessed via the + operator.This function is overridden by the compiler with an efficient implementation. This definition is\nthe logical model.Examples:* (7 : Int) + (6 : Int) = 13* (6 : Int) + (-6 : Int) = 0\n\nSubtraction of integers, usually accessed via the - operator.This function is overridden by the compiler with an efficient implementation. This definition is\nthe logical model.Examples:* (63 : Int) - (6 : Int) = 57* (7 : Int) - (0 : Int) = 7* (0 : Int) - (7 : Int) = -7\n\nNon-truncating subtraction of two natural numbers.Examples:* Int.subNatNat 5 2 = 3* Int.subNatNat 2 5 = -3* Int.subNatNat 0 13 = -13\n\nNegation of integers, usually accessed via the - prefix operator.This function is overridden by the compiler with an efficient implementation. This definition is\nthe logical model.Examples:* -(6 : Int) = -6* -(-6 : Int) = 6* (12 : Int).neg = -12\n\nNegation of natural numbers.Examples:* Int.negOfNat 6 = -6* Int.negOfNat 0 = 0\n\nMultiplication of integers, usually accessed via the * operator.This function is overridden by the compiler with an efficient implementation. This definition is\nthe logical model.Examples:* (63 : Int) * (6 : Int) = 378* (6 : Int) * (-6 : Int) = -36* (7 : Int) * (0 : Int) = 0\n\nPower of an integer to a natural number, usually accessed via the ^ operator.Examples:* (2 : Int) ^ 4 = 16* (10 : Int) ^ 0 = 1* (0 : Int) ^ 10 = 0* (-7 : Int) ^ 3 = -343\n\nComputes the greatest common divisor of two integers as a natural number. The GCD of two integers is\nthe largest natural number that evenly divides both. However, the GCD of a number and 0 is the\nnumber's absolute value.This implementation uses Nat.gcd, which is overridden in both the kernel and the compiler to\nefficiently evaluate using arbitrary-precision arithmetic.Examples:* Int.gcd 10 15 = 5* Int.gcd 10 (-15) = 5* Int.gcd (-6) (-9) = 3* Int.gcd 0 5 = 5* Int.gcd (-7) 0 = 7\n\nComputes the least common multiple of two integers as a natural number. The LCM of two integers is\nthe smallest natural number that's evenly divisible by the absolute values of both.Examples:* Int.lcm 9 6 = 18* Int.lcm 9 (-6) = 18* Int.lcm 9 3 = 9* Int.lcm 9 (-3) = 9* Int.lcm 0 3 = 0* Int.lcm (-3) 0 = 0\n\n\n\n","context":"Lean 参考\u0009基本类型\u0009整数\u0009API 参考","header":"20.2.4.3. 算术","id":"/____________/______/#zh-basictypes-int-h007"},"/____________/_________-inferBinderTypeFailed/#zh-errorexplanations-inferbindertypefailed-h001":{"contents":"Binder Type Requires New Type Variabledef identity x :=\n  x\nFailed to infer type of binder `x`\ndef identity (x : α) :=\n  x\n在上面的代码中，x的类型是不受约束的；如本示例所示，Lean 不\n自动为此类绑定器生成新的类型变量。相反，x 的类型 α 必须是\n明确指定。请注意，如果启用自动隐式参数插入（因为它是通过\n默认），α本身的binder不需要提供； Lean 将为此插入隐式绑定器\n自动参数。\n\nUninferred Binder Type Due to Resulting Type Annotationdef plusTwo x : Nat :=\n  x + 2\nFailed to infer type of binder `x`\n\nNote: Because this declaration's type has been explicitly provided, all parameter types and holes (e.g., `_`) in its header are resolved before its body is processed; information from the declaration body cannot be used to infer what these values should be\ndef plusTwo (x : Nat) : Nat :=\n  x + 2\n尽管 x 被推断为 plusTwo 主体中的类型为 Nat，但此信息不是\n在详细说明定义的类型时可用，因为其结果类型 (Nat) 已\n明确指定。仅考虑标头中的信息，无法确定 x 的类型\n确定，导致显示的错误。因此，有必要将 x 的类型包含在\n它的活页夹。\n\nAttempting to Name an Example Declarationexample trivial_proof : True :=\n  trivial\nFailed to infer type of binder `trivial_proof`\n\nNote: Examples do not have names. The identifier `trivial_proof` is being interpreted as a parameter `(trivial_proof : _)`.\nexample : True :=\n  trivial\n此代码无效，因为它尝试为 example 声明指定名称。例子不能\n被命名，并且在其他声明形式中出现名称的地方写入标识符\n被详细精化为粘合剂，其类型无法推断。如果必须命名声明，则应该是\n使用支持命名的声明形式定义，例如 def 或 theorem。\n\nAttempting to Define Multiple Opaque Constants at Onceopaque m n : Nat\nFailed to infer type of binder `n`\n\nNote: Multiple constants cannot be declared in a single declaration. The identifier `n` is being interpreted as a parameter `(n : _)`.\nopaque m : Nat\nopaque n : Nat\n此示例错误地尝试使用单个 opaque 声明定义多个常量。\n这样的声明只能定义一个常量：不可能列出多个标识符\n在 opaque 或 def 之后将它们定义为具有相同的类型（或值）。这样的声明是\n相反，详细说明为使用由给出的参数定义单个常量（例如上面的 m）\n后续标识符 (n)，其类型未指定且无法推断。定义多个\n全局常量，需要单独声明。\n\nAttempting to Define Multiple Structure Fields on the Same Linestructure Person where\n  givenName familyName : String\n  age : Nat\nFailed to infer type of binder `familyName`\nstructure Person where\n  givenName : String\n  familyName : String\n  age : Nat\nstructure Person where\n  (givenName familyName : String)\n  age : Nat\n此示例错误地尝试定义多个结构字段（givenName 和 familyName）\n通过在同一行连续列出它们来表示同一类型。 Lean 相反将其解释为\n定义单个字段 givenName，由没有指定类型的绑定器 familyName 参数化。\n可以通过在单独的行上列出每个字段或将每个字段括起来来实现预期的行为\n在括号中指定多个字段名称的行（请参阅手册部分\n归纳类型 了解有关结构的更多详细信息\n声明）。\n\n","context":"Lean 参考\u0009错误说明\u0009关于： inferBinderTypeFailed","header":"示例","id":"/____________/_________-inferBinderTypeFailed/#zh-errorexplanations-inferbindertypefailed-h001"},"/____________/_______________/#ByteArray":{"contents":"字节数组是一种特殊的数组类型，只能包含 UInt8 类型的元素。\n由于此限制，它们可以使用更有效的表示形式，而无需指针间接寻址。\n与其他数组一样，字节数组在编译代码中表示为 动态数组，Lean 运行时专门优化了数组操作。\n修改字节数组的操作首先检查该数组的引用计数，如果没有其他对该数组的引用，则就地修改。\n\n字节数组没有文字语法。\nList.toByteArray 可用于从列表文字构造数组。\n\nByteArray is like Array UInt8, but with an efficient run-time representation as a packed\nbyte buffer.Packs an array of bytes into a ByteArray.Converting between Array and ByteArray takes linear time.The data contained in the byte array.Converting between Array and ByteArray takes linear time.\n\n\n\n","context":"Lean 参考\u0009基本类型","header":"20.17. 字节吞吐量","id":"/____________/_______________/#ByteArray"},"/releases/v4.19.0/#markdown-14911236682459246477-h13":{"contents":"* #7312 implements proof term generation for cooper_dvd_left and its\nvariants in the cutsat procedure for linear integer arithmetic.* #7315 implements the Cooper conflict resolution in cutsat. We still\nneed to implement the backtracking and disequality case.* #7339 implements cooper conflict resolution in the cutsat procedure.\nIt also fixes several bugs in the proof term construction. We still need\nto add more tests, but we can already solve the following example that\nomega fails to solve:example (x y : Int) :\n    27 ≤ 11*x + 13*y →\n    11*x + 13*y ≤ 45 →\n    -10 ≤ 7*x - 9*y →\n    7*x - 9*y ≤ 4 → 假 := 通过\n  磨\n* #7351 ensures cutsat does not have to perform case analysis in the\nunivariate polynomial case. That it, it can close a goal whenever there\nis no solution for a divisibility constraint in an interval. Example of\ntheorem that is now proved in a single step by cutsat:example (x : Int) : 100 ≤ x → x ≤ 10000 → 20000 ∣ 3*x → False := by\n  磨\n* #7357 adds support for / and % to the cutsat procedure.* #7369 uses let-declarations for each polynomial occurring in a proof\nterm generated by the cutsat procedure.* #7370 simplifies the proof term due to the Cooper's conflict\nresolution in cutsat.* #7373 implements the last missing case for the cutsat procedure and\nfixes a bug. During model construction, we may encounter a bounded\ninterval containing integer solutions that satisfy the divisibility\nconstraint but fail to satisfy known disequalities.* #7394 adds infrastructure necessary for supporting Nat in the cutsat\nprocedure. It also makes the grind more robust.* #7396 fixes a bug in the cutsat model construction. It was searching\nfor a solution in the wrong direction.* #7401 improves the cutsat model search procedure by tightening\ninequalities using divisibility constraints.* #7494 implements support for Nat inequalities in the cutsat\nprocedure.* #7495 implements support for Nat divisibility constraints in the\ncutsat procedure.* #7501 implements support for Nat equalities and disequalities in the\ncutsat procedure.* #7502 implements support for Nat div and mod in the cutsat\nprocedure.* #7503 implements support for Nat.sub in cutsat* #7536 implements support for ¬ d ∣ p in the cutsat procedure.* #7537 implements support for Int.natAbs and Int.toNat in the\ncutsat procedure.* #7538 fixes a bug in the cutsat model construction. It was not\nresetting the decision stack at the end of the search.* #7561 fixes the support for nonlinear Nat terms in cutsat. For\nexample, cutsat was failing in the following exampleexample (i j k l : Nat) : i / j + k + l - k = i / j + l := by grind\nbecause we were not adding the fact that i / j is non negative when we\ninject the Nat expression into Int.* #7579 improves the counterexamples produced by the cutsat procedure,\nand adds proper support for Nat. Before this PR, the assignment for an\nnatural variable x would be represented as NatCast.natCast x.\n\n","context":"Lean 参考\u0009发行说明\u0009Lean 4.19.0 (2025-05-01)\u0009Language","header":"CutSat","id":"/releases/v4.19.0/#markdown-14911236682459246477-h13"},"/releases/v4.19.0/#markdown-14911236682459246477-h22":{"contents":"* #7198 使 Char 命名空间中的文档字符串遵循\n文档约定。* #7204 添加 Id monad 的文档字符串。* #7246 更新 Bool 的现有文档字符串并添加缺失的文档字符串。* #7288 修复了 List.removeAll 的文档* #7365 更新文档字符串并添加一些缺失的内容。* #7452 使出现在\n语言参考一致。* #7476 添加 IO 缺失的文档字符串和相关代码，并使\n与现有文档字符串的风格一致。* #7492 添加缺失的 Array 文档字符串并使其风格\n一致。* #7506 添加缺失的 String 文档字符串并生成现有文档字符串\n风格一致。* #7523 添加缺失的文档字符串并使文档字符串样式保持一致\nSystem 和 System.FilePath。* #7528 使 Thunk 的文档字符串与\n其他人。* #7534 添加缺失的 Syntax 相关文档字符串并使现有的\n与其他风格一致的。* #7535 修改了 funext 的文档字符串，使其更加简洁和\n添加对手册的参考以获取更多详细信息。* #7548 添加缺失的 monad 转换器文档字符串并使其风格\n一致。* #7552 添加了缺失的 Nat 文档字符串并使其风格保持一致。* #7564 更新了 ULift 和 PLift 的文档字符串，使其\n风格与其他一致。* #7568 添加缺失的 Int 文档字符串并制作所有文档字符串的样式\n一致。* #7602 添加 固定位宽整数 操作缺少的文档字符串\n使他们的风格保持一致。* #7607 添加 String.drop 和 String.dropRight 的文档字符串。* #7613 为出现在\n手册。* #7635 为 Substring 添加缺失的文档字符串，并使样式为\nSubstring 文档字符串一致。* #7642 查看 Float 和 Float32 的文档字符串，添加缺失的内容\n并使其格式一致。* #7645 添加缺失的文档字符串并使文档字符串样式保持一致\nForM、ForIn、ForIn'、ForInStep、IntCast 和 NatCast。* #7711 添加了手册中最后几个缺失的文档字符串。* #7713 使 BitVec 文档字符串彼此匹配以及其余部分匹配\nAPI 时尚。\n\n","context":"Lean 参考\u0009发行说明\u0009Lean 4.19.0 (2025-05-01)","header":"文档","id":"/releases/v4.19.0/#markdown-14911236682459246477-h22"},"/releases/v4.26.0/#markdown-13247546207354964368-h17":{"contents":"* #10787 改进了服务器日志记录机制以允许过滤日志\n通过 LSP 方法输出。* #10805 将字段 isDisplayableTerm 添加到 TermInfo 和所有实用程序\n创建 TermInfo 的函数可以设置为强制语言\n服务器在悬停弹出窗口中呈现术语。\n\n","context":"Lean 参考\u0009发行说明\u0009Lean 4.26.0 (2025-12-13)","header":"服务器","id":"/releases/v4.26.0/#markdown-13247546207354964368-h17"}});